==人口==
大薩德伯里是安大略省北部人口最多的城鎮和[[按人口排列的加拿大大都會區列表|普查都會區]]。據2016年人口普查，市内人口為161531人，較2011年的160274人增長0.8%。居民歲數中位數為41.1歲，較安省平均的39.0歲略高<ref name="www12.statcan.gc.ca">{{cite web|url=http://www12.statcan.gc.ca/census-recensement/2006/dp-pd/prof/92-591/details/page.cfm?Lang=E&Geo1=CSD&Code1=3553005&Geo2=PR&Code2=35&Data=Count&SearchText=greater%20sudbury&SearchType=Begins&SearchPR=01&B1=All&Custom=|title=Statistics Canada: 2006 Community Profiles|first=Government of Canada, Statistics|last=Canada|publisher=|accessdate=April 9, 2017|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304035632/http://www12.statcan.gc.ca/census-recensement/2006/dp-pd/prof/92-591/details/page.cfm?Lang=E&Geo1=CSD&Code1=3553005&Geo2=PR&Code2=35&Data=Count&SearchText=greater%20sudbury&SearchType=Begins&SearchPR=01&B1=All&Custom=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

市内40%居民能以[[加拿大法語|法語]]溝通。在家使用英語的居民佔全市80.1%，法語則達16.3%，遠高於安省平均的2.4%<ref>{{cite web |last =Statistics Canada |title =2006 Community Profile |year =2006 |url =http://www12.statcan.gc.ca/census-recensement/2006/dp-pd/prof/92-591/details/page.cfm?Lang=E&Geo1=CSD&Code1=3553005&Geo2=PR&Code2=35&Data=Count&SearchText=greater%20sudbury&SearchType=Begins&SearchPR=01&B1=All&Custom= |accessdate =2011-08-28 |archive-date =2016-03-04 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160304035632/http://www12.statcan.gc.ca/census-recensement/2006/dp-pd/prof/92-591/details/page.cfm?Lang=E&Geo1=CSD&Code1=3553005&Geo2=PR&Code2=35&Data=Count&SearchText=greater%20sudbury&SearchType=Begins&SearchPR=01&B1=All&Custom= |dead-url =no }}</ref>。2011年，市内81%居民為基督徒（天主教徒達59%），18%居民沒有宗教信仰，而穆斯林、猶太教徒和印度教徒則合共佔全市人口約1%<ref name="Statistics Canada 2011">{{cite web | last =Statistics Canada | title =2011 National Household Survey | year =2011 | url =http://www12.statcan.gc.ca/nhs-enm/2011/dp-pd/prof/details/page.cfm?Lang=E&Geo1=CSD&Code1=3553005&Data=Count&SearchText=greater%20sudbury&SearchType=Begins&SearchPR=01&A1=All&B1=All&Custom=&TABID=1 | accessdate =2013-08-30 | archive-date =2013-12-11 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20131211131413/http://www12.statcan.gc.ca/nhs-enm/2011/dp-pd/prof/details/page.cfm?Lang=E&Geo1=CSD&Code1=3553005&Data=Count&SearchText=greater%20sudbury&SearchType=Begins&SearchPR=01&A1=All&B1=All&Custom=&TABID=1 | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

2016年大薩德伯里{{percent|5,990|158,665|1}}居民為[[可見少數族裔|可見少數族裔]]，低於全國平均的{{percent|7,674,580|34,460,065|1}}，但市内[[加拿大原住民|原住民]]比例（{{percent|19,785|158,665|1}}）則高於全國平均的{{percent|2,130,520|34,460,065|1}}。佔全市人口多於0.5%的可見少數族裔如下：0.9%為南亞人、0.9%為黑人、0.6%為[[加拿大華人|華人]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www12.statcan.gc.ca/census-recensement/2016/dp-pd/prof/details/page.cfm?Lang=E&Geo1=CSD&Code1=3553005&Geo2=CD&Code2=3553&SearchText=greater+sud&SearchType=Begins&SearchPR=01&B1=All&TABID=1&type=1|title=Census Profile, 2016 Census - Greater Sudbury, City [Census subdivision], Ontario and Greater Sudbury, Census division [Census division], Ontario|last=Government of Canada|first=Statistics Canada|date=2017-02-08|website=www12.statcan.gc.ca|access-date=2019-07-16|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801073024/https://www12.statcan.gc.ca/census-recensement/2016/dp-pd/prof/details/page.cfm?Lang=E&Geo1=CSD&Code1=3553005&Geo2=CD&Code2=3553&SearchText=greater+sud&SearchType=Begins&SearchPR=01&B1=All&TABID=1&type=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年大薩德伯里17.2%居民擁有大學學位，低於全國平均的23.3%。沒有任何專上學院證書或文憑的居民則佔全市人口18.1%，略高於全國平均的17.3%<ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite web|url=http://www12.statcan.gc.ca/nhs-enm/2011/as-sa/fogs-spg/Pages/FOG.cfm?lang=E&level=3&GeoCode=580|title=Greater Sudbury / Grand Sudbury (CMA) - Focus on Geography Series - 2011 National Household Survey (NHS)|last=Canada|first=Government of Canada, Statistics|publisher=|accessdate=April 9, 2017|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807043301/https://www12.statcan.gc.ca/nhs-enm/2011/as-sa/fogs-spg/Pages/FOG.cfm?lang=E&level=3&GeoCode=580|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

